a really strong papa.

00:12:04.933 --> 00:12:07.060 position:50% align:center
And... Yue.

00:12:07.143 --> 00:12:09.646 position:50% align:center
You're strong, so I wanna
be just like you!

00:12:09.729 --> 00:12:12.607 position:50% align:center
The strongest, coolest,
prettiest big sister!

00:12:12.691 --> 00:12:14.901 position:50% align:center
Myu, why?

00:12:14.984 --> 00:12:15.985 position:50% align:center
Myu.

00:12:16.069 --> 00:12:17.862 position:50% align:center
You're such a
perfect little angel.

00:12:17.946 --> 00:12:19.698 position:50% align:center
Oh, uh, thanks.

00:12:19.781 --> 00:12:21.157 position:50% align:center
Myu, look here!

00:12:21.241 --> 00:12:23.410 position:50% align:center
I'm cool and strong too,
don'tcha think?

00:12:23.493 --> 00:12:25.829 position:50% align:center
I can pulverize enemies
with one blow!

00:12:25.912 --> 00:12:28.373 position:50% align:center
