into mincemeat!

00:12:28.456 --> 00:12:29.499 position:50% align:center
[SHEA grunts]

00:12:29.582 --> 00:12:30.917 position:50% align:center
Hey, Myu!

00:12:31.001 --> 00:12:33.670 position:50% align:center
This big sister is really good
at binding her enemies!

00:12:33.753 --> 00:12:37.382 position:50% align:center
You wanna see my rapid-fire
Binding Blades of Light?

00:12:37.465 --> 00:12:39.759 position:50% align:center
Would you like to see my
formidable breath attack?

00:12:39.843 --> 00:12:41.636 position:50% align:center
You are not going
to believe your eyes!

