They will twinkle with the
light of a thousand stars!

00:12:45.140 --> 00:12:47.726 position:50% align:center
[GROUP chattering]

00:12:49.519 --> 00:12:51.604 position:50% align:center
Hey, big sisters?

00:12:51.688 --> 00:12:57.777 position:50% align:center
