so much cool as sloppy?

00:12:57.861 --> 00:12:59.070 position:50% align:center
[SHEA yells]

00:12:59.154 --> 00:13:01.865 position:50% align:center
Sorry, Big Sister
Kaori, but um,

00:13:01.948 --> 00:13:03.575 position:50% align:center
I think you're a little weak.

00:13:03.658 --> 00:13:05.118 position:50% align:center
[KAORI]
No!

00:13:05.201 --> 00:13:09.164 position:50% align:center
As for Big Sister Tio,
you're pretty okay.

00:13:09.247 --> 00:13:11.875 position:50% align:center
