00:13:22.344 --> 00:13:23.720 position:50% align:center
Ho ho ho!

00:13:23.803 --> 00:13:25.889 position:50% align:center
It seems like somebody
here needs a little lesson

00:13:25.972 --> 00:13:29.142 position:50% align:center
