you cross a dragon, huh?

00:13:29.225 --> 00:13:30.226 position:50% align:center
[YUE]
Heh.

00:13:33.813 --> 00:13:35.482 position:50% align:center
Uh, big sisters?

00:13:35.565 --> 00:13:36.941 position:50% align:center
Sweet Sister Kaori.

00:13:37.025 --> 00:13:38.360 position:50% align:center
Pretty Sister Shea.

00:13:38.443 --> 00:13:39.611 position:50% align:center
Strong Sister Tio.

00:13:39.694 --> 00:13:42.238 position:50% align:center
I think all your outfits
are great, too, honest!

00:13:42.322 --> 00:13:43.281 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Huh?

00:13:43.365 --> 00:13:45.825 position:50% align:center
So, um... let's see.

00:13:45.909 --> 00:13:47.202 position:50% align:center
I know!

00:13:47.285 --> 00:13:49.788 position:50% align:center
How about we all trade outfits
and see how we look?

00:13:49.871 --> 00:13:51.206 position:50% align:center
