00:13:51.289 --> 00:13:52.665 position:50% align:center
[MYU]
Yeah, come on!

00:13:52.749 --> 00:13:56.002 position:50% align:center
If we want to, we can all try
on each other's clothes!

00:13:56.086 --> 00:13:57.796 position:50% align:center
It'll be lots of fun!

00:14:00.048 --> 00:14:01.132 position:50% align:center
