00:14:07.472 --> 00:14:08.682 position:50% align:center
--Hajime!
--[TIO] Master, please.

00:14:08.765 --> 00:14:10.392 position:50% align:center
Each of you are different,
so you might need

00:14:10.475 --> 00:14:12.977 position:50% align:center
some minor alterations,
but I'm sure there are

00:14:13.061 --> 00:14:14.813 position:50% align:center
plenty of tailors in this town.

00:14:16.272 --> 00:14:18.525 position:50% align:center
Yeah, what Papa said!
Let's do it!

00:14:23.613 --> 00:14:26.157 position:50% align:center
[MYU]
Papa! Look, look!

00:14:26.241 --> 00:14:27.242 position:50% align:center
Oh...

00:14:33.415 --> 00:14:34.749 position:50% align:center
Nice, Myu.

00:14:34.833 --> 00:14:36.167 position:50% align:center
You look very grown-up in that.

00:14:38.586 --> 00:14:41.297 position:50% align:center
