going to come out together.

00:14:55.020 --> 00:14:57.147 position:50% align:center
Big Sister Yue,
you're so pretty!

00:14:57.230 --> 00:14:58.273 position:50% align:center
Why, thank you.

00:14:58.356 --> 00:14:59.816 position:50% align:center
[curtain opens]

00:15:02.110 --> 00:15:05.488 position:50% align:center
[TIO] Well. I've never worn
anything like this before.

00:15:05.572 --> 00:15:07.824 position:50% align:center
This feeling is certainly new.

00:15:11.077 --> 00:15:12.620 position:50% align:center
[SHEA] Kaori's outfit
has way more layers

00:15:12.704 --> 00:15:14.164 position:50% align:center
than I thought.

00:15:14.247 --> 00:15:17.042 position:50% align:center
How could anyone
move around in this?

00:15:17.125 --> 00:15:19.294 position:50% align:center
Tio, you look great, really.

00:15:22.297 --> 00:15:24.090 position:50% align:center
And you too, Shea.
Looks lovely.

00:15:24.174 --> 00:15:26.384 position:50% align:center
Thanks for saying so, Hajime.

00:15:26.468 --> 00:15:28.678 position:50% align:center
Big Sister Tio and
Big Sister Shea,

00:15:28.762 --> 00:15:30.221 position:50% align:center
you two look so cute!

00:15:33.099 --> 00:15:34.100 position:50% align:center
[HAJIME]
What about Kaori?

00:15:34.184 --> 00:15:35.185 position:50% align:center
Where is she?

00:15:35.268 --> 00:15:37.020 position:50% align:center
[YUE]
Right. She's still back there.

00:15:37.103 --> 00:15:38.563 position:50% align:center
I'll go drag her out.

00:15:38.646 --> 00:15:39.898 position:50% align:center
[HAJIME]
Yue?

00:15:39.981 --> 00:15:43.234 position:50% align:center
[KAORI gasps] No!
Shea's outfit is like nothing!

00:15:43.318 --> 00:15:45.362 position:50% align:center
I feel totally naked!

00:15:45.445 --> 00:15:46.446 position:50% align:center
[YUE]
We all did it.

00:15:46.529 --> 00:15:47.781 position:50% align:center
Don't chicken out!

00:15:47.864 --> 00:15:50.200 position:50% align:center
[KAORI] I can't! I can't!
You can't make me!

00:15:50.283 --> 00:15:52.118 position:50% align:center
[YUE]
Come on! Don't be like that!

00:16:04.381 --> 00:16:06.966 position:50% align:center
I'm exposed, nobody look at me!

00:16:07.050 --> 00:16:09.969 position:50% align:center
Especially not you,
Hajime, avert your eyes!

00:16:34.494 --> 00:16:37.414 position:50% align:center
[YUE] A merfolk girl, curled up
just like a little kitten,

00:16:37.497 --> 00:16:39.124 position:50% align:center
the cuteness is off the charts.

00:16:39.207 --> 00:16:40.208 position:50% align:center
I can't resist.

00:16:40.291 --> 00:16:41.334 position:50% align:center
I must pet her.

00:16:43.044 --> 00:16:44.421 position:50% align:center
[YUE]
I must be careful!

00:16:44.504 --> 00:16:47.382 position:50% align:center
I shall pet her using my
extreme, gentle petting skills!

00:16:47.465 --> 00:16:49.551 position:50% align:center
If I wake her, it's all over!

00:16:51.636 --> 00:16:52.762 position:50% align:center
[YUE chuckles]

00:16:53.346 --> 00:16:54.973 position:50% align:center
Uh-oh! I made a noise!

00:16:55.056 --> 00:16:56.725 position:50% align:center
I couldn't hold it!

00:16:58.476 --> 00:17:00.270 position:50% align:center
Her cuteness is almost scary.

00:17:00.353 --> 00:17:02.313 position:50% align:center
She's too precious.

00:17:05.608 --> 00:17:06.735 position:50% align:center
Wow, Yue.

00:17:06.818 --> 00:17:08.486 position:50% align:center
I've never seen you
make a face like that.

00:17:09.029 --> 00:17:10.905 position:50% align:center
Did you melt?
Cuz you've gone soft.

00:17:10.989 --> 00:17:13.408 position:50% align:center
You almost look like
some kind of pervert.

00:17:13.491 --> 00:17:16.578 position:50% align:center
[YUE] An actual pervert calling
me a dangerous pervert.

00:17:16.661 --> 00:17:18.038 position:50% align:center
The shame is unbearable.

00:17:18.121 --> 00:17:20.081 position:50% align:center
[HAJIME chuckles]

00:17:20.165 --> 00:17:22.917 position:50% align:center
Priceless. Totally priceless.

00:17:23.001 --> 00:17:25.003 position:50% align:center
To the max!

00:17:25.086 --> 00:17:28.131 position:50% align:center
[YUE] Hajime's using strange
words from his world again.

00:17:28.214 --> 00:17:30.675 position:50% align:center
