What's he talking about?

00:17:32.385 --> 00:17:33.845 position:50% align:center
Well, it doesn't matter.

00:17:35.430 --> 00:17:39.476 position:50% align:center
She did say yesterday that I'm
the coolest big sister, but...

00:17:39.559 --> 00:17:41.561 position:50% align:center
I have one gripe.

00:17:41.644 --> 00:17:43.313 position:50% align:center
