00:17:45.607 --> 00:17:46.608 position:50% align:center
And why not?

00:17:46.691 --> 00:17:49.361 position:50% align:center
Why not call me mama, Myu?

00:17:49.444 --> 00:17:52.072 position:50% align:center
I suppose, for Myu, her
real mother is her mama,

00:17:52.155 --> 00:17:53.239 position:50% align:center
so it makes sense.

00:17:53.323 --> 00:17:55.158 position:50% align:center
I get that, but...

00:17:55.241 --> 00:17:57.619 position:50% align:center
And yet,
I also don't get it!

00:17:57.702 --> 00:18:01.247 position:50% align:center
I think it's okay to have
more than one mama!

00:18:01.331 --> 00:18:03.249 position:50% align:center
In fact, having two mamas?

00:18:03.333 --> 00:18:05.710 position:50% align:center
Who could ask for a
better deal than that?

00:18:05.794 --> 00:18:07.671 position:50% align:center
Um, hold on, Yue.

00:18:07.754 --> 00:18:10.298 position:50% align:center
You can't make mothering
into a two-for-one deal.

00:18:10.382 --> 00:18:13.635 position:50% align:center
I think this is where we
say our piece quietly.

00:18:13.718 --> 00:18:16.429 position:50% align:center
And look, you woke up poor Myu.

00:18:16.513 --> 00:18:18.473 position:50% align:center
Wha--? Oh, no.

00:18:21.559 --> 00:18:22.852 position:50% align:center
Myu.

00:18:22.936 --> 00:18:25.063 position:50% align:center
Um, yes, what is it?

00:18:25.146 --> 00:18:26.523 position:50% align:center
Just forget what I said.

00:18:26.606 --> 00:18:29.025 position:50% align:center
"Big Sister Yue"
is quite satisfactory.

00:18:29.109 --> 00:18:30.610 position:50% align:center
Really, you can call me that.

00:18:33.405 --> 00:18:34.781 position:50% align:center
[YUE]
This is unbearable.

00:18:34.864 --> 00:18:37.742 position:50% align:center
This ranks in the top three
worst moments of my life.

00:18:37.826 --> 00:18:40.495 position:50% align:center
I wish the abyss would
swallow me whole.

00:18:41.955 --> 00:18:44.457 position:50% align:center
What would mama do right now?

00:18:44.541 --> 00:18:45.625 position:50% align:center
Right!

00:18:45.709 --> 00:18:48.753 position:50% align:center
My mama would want me to say.

00:18:48.837 --> 00:18:51.339 position:50% align:center
Big Sister Yue, I love you lots!

00:18:52.924 --> 00:18:55.635 position:50% align:center
You're so strong and
cool and pretty and nice.

00:18:55.719 --> 00:18:58.930 position:50% align:center
You're awesome!
You're the best!

00:18:59.014 --> 00:19:00.682 position:50% align:center
Thanks, Myu.

00:19:00.765 --> 00:19:01.933 position:50% align:center
What is this?

00:19:02.017 --> 00:19:04.185 position:50% align:center
This feeling, is it comfort?

00:19:04.269 --> 00:19:05.770 position:50% align:center
Like a mother's love?

00:19:05.854 --> 00:19:07.313 position:50% align:center
What is happening right now?

00:19:09.524 --> 00:19:12.193 position:50% align:center
My energy is being drained.

00:19:12.277 --> 00:19:14.863 position:50% align:center
If I had a mama just
like Big Sister Yue,

00:19:14.946 --> 00:19:17.365 position:50% align:center
that would be so awesome!

00:19:17.449 --> 00:19:20.618 position:50% align:center
But I already have a
mama, and I love her.

00:19:20.702 --> 00:19:22.537 position:50% align:center
She is my only mama.

00:19:24.581 --> 00:19:25.707 position:50% align:center
Oh, but wait!

00:19:25.790 --> 00:19:27.625 position:50% align:center
I don't have a real sister!

00:19:32.380 --> 00:19:33.715 position:50% align:center
[YUE]
Yes!

00:19:33.798 --> 00:19:35.800 position:50% align:center
I do want to be your big sister!

00:19:39.262 --> 00:19:41.222 position:50% align:center
I am your big sister now!

00:19:41.306 --> 00:19:43.183 position:50% align:center
Big Sister Yue!

00:19:43.266 --> 00:19:46.102 position:50% align:center
Thank you so much!

00:19:46.186 --> 00:19:49.147 position:50% align:center
[YUE]
Gah! Myu is petting me.

00:19:49.230 --> 00:19:51.107 position:50% align:center
What a healing experience!

00:19:51.191 --> 00:19:53.443 position:50% align:center
Big Sister forever!

00:19:53.526 --> 00:19:55.695 position:50% align:center
Whoa! Her cuteness melted Yue?

00:19:55.779 --> 00:19:56.905 position:50% align:center
Yes, indeed.

00:19:56.988 --> 00:19:58.782 position:50% align:center
It's terrifying.

00:19:58.865 --> 00:20:01.076 position:50% align:center
[TIO]
Myu's emanating maternal energy?

00:20:01.159 --> 00:20:04.913 position:50% align:center
And her power caused Yue to
regress to an infantile state?

00:20:04.996 --> 00:20:06.581 position:50% align:center
Impossible.

00:20:06.664 --> 00:20:08.541 position:50% align:center
"The Phe-mom-enon"
seems to be taking place

00:20:08.625 --> 00:20:10.960 position:50% align:center
right now between Myu and Yue.

00:20:11.044 --> 00:20:13.922 position:50% align:center
Master, you mean you've
witnessed something like this?

00:20:14.464 --> 00:20:15.715 position:50% align:center
Let me explain.

00:20:15.799 --> 00:20:17.509 position:50% align:center
In Japan, there's
a thing known as

00:20:17.592 --> 00:20:20.178 position:50% align:center
"feeling the Babumi
and going Ogya."

00:20:20.261 --> 00:20:21.888 position:50% align:center
Well, that sounds terrifying!

00:20:21.971 --> 00:20:23.306 position:50% align:center
I've never heard of it!

00:20:23.390 --> 00:20:25.892 position:50% align:center
Is that what's happening
between Yue and Myu?

00:20:25.975 --> 00:20:29.729 position:50% align:center
To sum it up, Myu is showing
an atypical motherly side,

00:20:29.813 --> 00:20:32.691 position:50% align:center
and all that maternal
energy is making Yue

00:20:32.774 --> 00:20:35.235 position:50% align:center
want to cuddle up
to Myu like her baby!

00:20:37.362 --> 00:20:38.780 position:50% align:center
This is gold.

00:20:38.863 --> 00:20:40.824 position:50% align:center
So hilariously priceless!

00:20:40.907 --> 00:20:43.910 position:50% align:center
The roles reversed like that?
It's ridiculous!

00:20:43.993 --> 00:20:46.162 position:50% align:center
We are witnessing
Master's breakdown.

00:20:46.246 --> 00:20:48.748 position:50% align:center
The man is falling apart
right before our very eyes!

00:20:48.832 --> 00:20:50.250 position:50% align:center
Yes, I see.

00:20:50.333 --> 00:20:52.794 position:50% align:center
Hajime's mental state does
seem to be disproportionately

00:20:52.877 --> 00:20:55.171 position:50% align:center
affected by anything
related to Yue.

00:20:55.255 --> 00:20:58.174 position:50% align:center
And what happened just now
was pretty extraordinary.

00:20:58.258 --> 00:20:59.551 position:50% align:center
A full reversal.

00:20:59.634 --> 00:21:01.970 position:50% align:center
Yue was in mother mode
and Myu was baby.

00:21:02.053 --> 00:21:04.597 position:50% align:center
Now Myu is the mom
and Yue is baby!

00:21:04.681 --> 00:21:06.016 position:50% align:center
It's crazy!

00:21:06.099 --> 00:21:08.351 position:50% align:center
[TIO] And Master's psyche
couldn't hold out against

00:21:08.435 --> 00:21:10.979 position:50% align:center
an adorability assault
of such magnitude!

00:21:12.981 --> 00:21:15.775 position:50% align:center
[YUE] I understand the appeal
of being a big sister, too,

00:21:15.859 --> 00:21:18.361 position:50% align:center
but the pull of motherhood
is so powerful!

00:21:18.445 --> 00:21:21.114 position:50% align:center
And yet, if I can't
be Myu's mama...

00:21:23.950 --> 00:21:25.869 position:50% align:center
...then perhaps I should
start thinking seriously

00:21:25.952 --> 00:21:28.580 position:50% align:center
about having my own baby.

00:21:28.663 --> 00:21:30.582 position:50% align:center
The journey continues.

00:21:30.665 --> 00:21:32.417 position:50% align:center
I can't jump Hajime's bones--

00:21:32.500 --> 00:21:34.961 position:50% align:center
I mean, I can't start my happy
family plan with Hajime

00:21:35.045 --> 00:21:37.297 position:50% align:center
right at this second.

00:21:37.380 --> 00:21:40.050 position:50% align:center
I have enough self-control
to understand that much.

00:21:40.133 --> 00:21:42.135 position:50% align:center
At the same time,
I can't keep using Myu

00:21:42.218 --> 00:21:44.637 position:50% align:center
as an outlet for my
maternal instincts!

00:21:47.057 --> 00:21:48.058 position:50% align:center
Hajime.

00:21:48.141 --> 00:21:50.560 position:50% align:center
[HAJIME]
Hm?

00:21:50.643 --> 00:21:52.103 position:50% align:center
Go "ogya?"

00:21:52.187 --> 00:21:53.772 position:50% align:center
[HAJIME]
Ogya?!

00:21:53.855 --> 00:21:56.107 position:50% align:center
[GROUP yells]

00:21:56.191 --> 00:21:57.359 position:50% align:center
Hold up!

00:21:57.442 --> 00:21:59.652 position:50% align:center
You cannot be saying you
want me to be the baby!

00:21:59.736 --> 00:22:02.739 position:50% align:center
You should know
that's not how I roll!

00:22:02.822 --> 00:22:04.199 position:50% align:center
[YUE chuckles]

00:22:05.492 --> 00:22:09.621 position:50% align:center
[GROUP yells]

00:22:09.704 --> 00:22:12.499 position:50% align:center
[HAJIME]
Ogya!